headline.main: NEW CELEBRITY ISSUES TO WOO NONCOLLECTORS

results.snippet: LEAD: FAMOUS entertainers are being employed by worldwide postal administrations and their philatelic agencies in their search for new avenues to reach millions of noncollectors. The entertainers are not used as one might expect - in paid commercials...
results.lead_paragraph: LEAD: FAMOUS entertainers are being employed by worldwide postal administrations and their philatelic agencies in their search for new avenues to reach millions of noncollectors. The entertainers are not used as one might expect - in paid commercials or testimonials. Rather, they are being increasingly chosen as subjects for stamp issues.
